source: BLS Job Openings and Labor Turnover Survey (JOLTS)
description: Monthly seasonally adjusted job openings, hires, and separations data for 12 industries, 2025. Levels in thousands; rates as percent of employment.

data_elements.name: Job Openings
data_elements.description: Unfilled positions on the last business day of the month

data_elements.name: Hires
data_elements.description: Workers added to payroll during the month

data_elements.name: Total Separations
data_elements.description: Workers who left or were removed from payroll during the month

data_elements.name: Quits
data_elements.description: Workers who left voluntarily (excludes retirements and transfers)

data_elements.name: Layoffs and Discharges
data_elements.description: Involuntary separations initiated by the employer
